The Database design (JSON tree structure) is as follows and carries all operations in O(1) time.

Users:
  uid:
    name: Gaurav
    blood_group: B+
    state:  XYZ
    district: ABC
    phone_no: 0987654321
    email: abc@mail.com
    time:1-3PM
    date: 20-08-2020
    hid: hospital_id_1
Donors:
  State1:
    District1: 
      uid1
      uid2
  State2:
    District2:
      uid3
      uid4
User_list:
  hid1:
    uid1
    uid2
    uid3
  hid2:
    uid4
    uid5
